{"tid":47060,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"必須旗幟鮮明地反對新icon","createTime":"2016-12-20T05:44:36.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T10:52:47.000Z","uid":55575,"like":29,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c70261a9f0c56189ad2f280ded9c73e42c7596b3","tid":47060,"uid":55575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T05:44:36.000Z","msg":"全連登用戶都要充分認識肥婆icon出現的嚴重性，團結起來，旗幟鮮明地反對新icon，堅決維護得來不易的安定團結的新論壇局面。<br />\n<br />\n決不允許容忍任何高登打手；對以任何借口推出新icon以分化連登的的行為要堅決制止；對蓄意造謠進行分化者，追究責任；<br />\n<br />\n要保護會員使用乾淨論壇的正當權利。廣大連登仔真誠地希望連登不要走回高登的舊路，這也是連尼住和admin的要求，這些要求只能在admin的領導下，加強治理整頓，積極推進改革，健全的連登民主和法制來實現。<br />\n<br />\n全連登管理層，全連登會員必須清醒地認識到，不堅決地鏟除新icon，將永無寧日，這場鬥爭事關連登的成敗，事關連登仔的前途。<br />\n<br />\n連登各級組織、廣大連登管理層、愛連登的人士和全連登會員要明辨是非，積極行動起來，為堅決、迅速地剷除這些骯髒的肥婆icon！😤"},{"pid":"64ad5436a1ff25ff3637ab39903ffec469a0a2f3","tid":47060,"uid":61954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T05:54:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fatc"},{"pid":"6fc54f1b9d732b805ef705633d5b656ebb608adc","tid":47060,"uid":55575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T06:00:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fatc</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n😤😤😤"},{"pid":"1c9e391cc14ddb8f12f45f7790065bb33e56ac25","tid":47060,"uid":19728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T06:02:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fatc</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n🖕🖕🖕"},{"pid":"7fb339b0c9b420c373e9fcd3696d0aabeaec303f","tid":47060,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T06:07:08.000Z","msg":"三反五反？"},{"pid":"eb1d0b5fc766b49f2e80cbd7bdf7652eeb6c984b","tid":47060,"uid":55575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T06:16:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fatc</bl